\textbackslash{}ldots +
\textbackslash{}left.\textbackslash{}left.\textbackslash{}frac\{1\}\{2+\textbackslash{}left(
1+\textbackslash{}frac\{(n-1)(x-1)\}\{n\} \textbackslash{}right)\^{}3\}
\textbackslash{}right\textbackslash{}\} \textbackslash{}frac\{x-1\}\{n\}
\textbackslash{}right{]} where \emph{x} $\geq$ 0. Find the equation of
